data.description: Welcome to this Amazing Well-Kept Home! Featuring three bedrooms, bonus room with Double glass Door, two full baths, utility room, attached two car garage, covered patio and wood privacy fence.  Kitchen with granite counter tops, black appliances, and nice size pantry open to Formal and spacious dining room. Living room with a corner stone/rock fireplace. Main bedroom is very specious with walk in closet and double doors to bath with double sink, garden tub, and separate shower. There is a double gate on the house right side fence to access backyard. Other amenities rain gutters, Water softener in garage. Roof was replaced March 2023. Bonus room can be den or office.
